

PIRASO

   This word is from the Spanish pedazo.

   piraso
   piece, bit, fragment, portion

   isang piraso
   one piece

   malaking piraso
   large piece

   maliit na piraso
   small piece

   isang malaking piraso ng aking puso
   a big piece of my heart

   Dalawang piraso ang natira.
   Two pieces were left.

   pira-piraso
   pieces, bits, fragments
